  "text": "Clustering analysis based on WC-MS data of the isolates was carried out with MALDI Biotyper software (Bruker Daltonics). This software performs clustering analysis using a highly sophisticated pattern-matching algorithm. The result of the clustering analysis of 222 isolates (including those previously isolated, [CITATION_1] ) and all available type strains is shown in Fig. 3 .",
